Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:09.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll become a different Banri and start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I feel like I've suddenly become free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:22.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:24.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me do something to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I see your friend at the hospital,\NI'll give him a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:34.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I promise I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:41.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, you shouldn't come here alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:43.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your signal will reach him eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:59.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's too late for my signal to reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't make it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...I can do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All I can think is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,if I had made it in time, that wouldn't have happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:22.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I had made it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I would have held his hand tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:28.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...and never let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:35.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your message?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell him, "You can do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to say that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Again? Why do I keep having that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:05.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...did Linda say to me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:17.82,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(251,293)}Summer Has Come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:27.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, if we could meet in a dream, could I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:52.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Say, if sadness alone floats down from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:03:00.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If that kind of voice pains you even now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if, off to the side, our hands are placed on each other's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:08.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This memory wouldn't fade, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:16.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if, when our eyes meet, I can't say the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:20.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your words illuminate the world more than anyone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:24.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Next to me, "Goodbye means I love you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be forthright
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Though I alone sing of loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't smile
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Thank you means I'm in love with you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The world's end of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The time came for our first event of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:58.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's the Awa dance festival the festival club is participating in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:04.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Other universities and Awa dance preservation societies are here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, they look like girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:19.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There are girls in our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so hot... Fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you guys can hang around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The building's air conditioned, and it feels great inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We let you use that space so you could change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:42.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're matching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Today I'm a beautiful woman dressed as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so handsome today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, you really do look better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can tell I'm not used to these clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's a battle of charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, your girlfriend's having a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:21.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a hunk of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's a modern day Yaoya Oshichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:33.23,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,45)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Note: Yaoya Oshichi was a woman who lived in the Edo period of Japan. In
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:33.23,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(379,73)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}an ill-advised attempt to get the attention of the man she was in love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:33.23,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(377,101)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}with, she tried to set a building on fire, but was caught by police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,45)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Note: (Cont'd) The joke here casts Kouko's decidedly humorous situation in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(106,73)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}that of a classic tragic heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Isn't this a job for her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:38.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is it heat stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She had lots of energy until a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Th-they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:58.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just n-nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:01.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:02.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sh-she's walking funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've already been to the bathroom about thirty times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,N-now that you mention it, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your bladder's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's nothing in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen to me. Calm down and think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your urge to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My urge to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...is a phantom urge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A phantom urge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Try to calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's even more of a hunk of junk than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like she's out of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's put on your lipstick, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, Roboko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Roboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't forget how funny you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:32.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Adieu, Roboko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:34.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:37.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'd leave one of our own behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kosshi-senpai, hasn't the time come to teach the first years about "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"That," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:53.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're going to do "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
