Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:06.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:14.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go to our first festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good work, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're dismissed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's a fireworks show later at the riverbank near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Feel free to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Changing's too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's at least change into sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The next time we meet will be at camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You danced well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm a ghost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:20.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My feelings for Linda still remain in Banri's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.90,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(210,92)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}STUPID LINDA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.90,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(372,318)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Baka Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:34.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Until now, I've thought of him as my younger twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if he didn't notice me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:42.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought he respected the feelings\NI had always nurtured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But he abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kouko, have you been to a fireworks show before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even though he still has feelings for Linda, he's forced himself to pretend there's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The booming explosions are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He rejected the feelings I had to leave behind in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll become an evil spirit and make you unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:08.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It suddenly started raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've gotta hurry up and find shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:32.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:37.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The seminar house we got for our camp is closed for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:38.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you in September.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:41.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been like this since summer vacation started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The fireworks display was canceled,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I missed the film showing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and Yana-san suddenly canceled our plans to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,On top of that, it's so hot every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, my lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm a surprising woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You took the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I sprinted up them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:01.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I could surprise you as you came to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were surprised, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.81,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(207,412)}And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And that's the spice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And that's the spice of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because of that, I ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:21.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make you a curried yakisoba that's so delicious, it'll blow your pain away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:21.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bought ingredients,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and I'm ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Great! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:41.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It looks fantastic on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bet you wear that whenever you cook at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well... yeah, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so girly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You really are a surprising girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love it! Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll help you with whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't have to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to make it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a girl thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So please, just sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:19.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I might need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why do I have to wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:38.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No reason. No reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, put your hands here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:45.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you take them out, it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,By the way, Banri, do you know about that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In a snowy village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:03.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,there's a middle-aged man living an ecological, healthy, and sustainable life with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:05.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...is having sexual relations with a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sexual...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But that's not the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's important is the sad truth that the man is a peeping Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:28.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The bird is chirping suspiciously... chirp, chirp, chirp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and acting strangely behind the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:33.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The man can't contain his curiosity, and in the end, he commits the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:39.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,his strange but happy life with the bird comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the Crane Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Put simply, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In other words... um... it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't watch you while you cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a terrible storyteller...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:58.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In any case, you'll make me really nervous if you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good! Face the other way and don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll do my very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My curried yakisoba will be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:18.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,By the way, Banri, did you hear our trip was canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's too bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:26.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought we could reminisce about the time we got lost in those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think that was such a fun memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:36.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, camp or no camp, we'll always be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Time to wash some vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:44.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Time to cut some vegetables and meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Time to sauté some vegetables and meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Time to add the noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:19.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now I'll season them and quickly finish them off like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look forward to-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,K-Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:33.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'll burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:48.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't what you think it is, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my best joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Air yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Air yakisoba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Laugh, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Try laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.24,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(204,412)}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.37,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(199,415)}This is the spice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the spice of love, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really meant to make it myself, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But while practicing at home,\NI started getting nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and I couldn't even hold a knife properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so weak under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:31.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So then our maid saw me and started making it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:34.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Saying, "You're useless! Give me that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:38.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm amazed she called her employer's daughter "useless."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She has a foul mouth, but she's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She even lent me this apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:51.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, can we talk a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll attend a proper cooking school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:00.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Normal's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Normal's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to make you think, "She's awesome!\NHer feminine charm is through the roof!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,maybe I'll throw myself into the culinary tiger's den and train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Culinary tiger's den?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and cancel my family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Barcelona, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A long vacation sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But... Banri, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:40.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if you spent the summer with me, you'd just be bored killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:46.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wish we could be together the whole time too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:49.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:51.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,L-let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Banri, you're forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry! Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Don't go to Barcelona. Stay with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't tell her to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:28.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can't complain if she abandons you eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:34.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Someday a better man will appear, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:40.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Find someone who can make you some delicious curried yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:47.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make you even unhappier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're wrong, I'm telling you you're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:18.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, you still don't notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:24.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Though I've wanted to touch that arm for the past two or three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:27.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:38.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The urge to scream is so great that, look, I can't stand it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:44.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So why, why won't you notice even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:51.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you really, really in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:57.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't need words of flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Love me semi-eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:04.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After 5,000 years or so, I won't be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not endless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:10.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I will die someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:17.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Being told "I'll love you forever" won't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:20.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, think only that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:25.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll love me till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:40.80,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,370)}Ladies Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:27.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love your air yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Forget about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:31.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:35.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want it to be our secret. It's a girl thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:39.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is...! The spice...! Of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:40.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
